OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry start with bright spells
OL,6,Fin the east but cloudy with rain in
OL,7,Fwest. Cloud and rain spreading to all
OL,8,Fparts through the day, heaviest rain
OL,9,Fin the west.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,12,Fdry and breezy on Friday and Saturday
OL,13,Fwith sunny spells and some showers
OL,14,Fpossible. Dry on Sunday with long
OL,15,Fperiods of sunshine developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
